main.pt-60.news
    .container
        .mb-60
            a(href="#").return-link
                .return-link--icon
                    +svg('arrow-left')
                .return-link--text
                    | Все новости
        .mb-60.text-center
            h1.h2 22-летие сети салонов Caterina Leman в России
        .news__detail.mb-120
            .row.justify-content-center
                .col-xl-8.col-md-10.col-md-12
                    +lazyPicture({
                        src: '/images/pages/news/newsDetail.jpg',
                        alt: '',
                    }).mb-12.news__detail-img
                    .news__detail-info.mb-24
